 (360,1,'2010-02-11 00:00:00','2010-02-10 23:00:00','<p>they are based in berlin and produce music that might be described as pumping, popped out, strangely addictive electronic bon-bons. they specialize in twisted vocals and freaky beats which they display in a hard, hot and happy live set.  Shitkatapult will release their new album IT\'S DARK BUT IT\'S OKAY the 19th of March worldwide.</p><p>Here are some links to check them out:</p><p><a title=\"Homepage\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.noticnastic.com\">www.noticnastic.com</a> <br /><a title=\"Myspace page\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.myspace.com/noticnastic\">www.myspace.com/noticnastic</a> <br /><a title=\"Youtube page\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/noticnastic \">www.youtube.com/noticnastic&nbsp;</a> </p>','NEW SIGNING','Random Noize Musick welcomes a new artist: NOTIC NASTIC, some anonymous electronic music machine from berlin and new york.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',30,'post','',0),
 (361,1,'2010-02-19 00:00:00','2010-02-18 23:00:00','','NEW VIDEO','As a preview to our soon coming album \"Ever Since\" by Xenia Beliayeva take a look at the video of the titletrack. Just simply doubleclick on the headline. The 12\" is out now, the album will be released 21st of May.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2010-04-26 00:00:00','2010-04-25 23:00:00','',0,'',31,'post','',0),
 (362,1,'2010-02-19 00:00:00','2010-02-18 23:00:00','','MOTOR EP OUT SOON','After the huge success of their latest album \"Metal Machine\" MOTOR are coming back with a digital-only EP \"Autokill/Pitch123\". This release will hit the streets the 12th of March 2010 and it\'s gonna mark the first release on Shitkatapult this year.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',32,'post','',0),
 (363,1,'2010-02-23 00:00:00','2010-02-22 23:00:00','Since the mid nineties initially in the artistic area for private views or similar on the move as a DJ, Xenia Beliayeva opened for Kraftwerk with Laurent Garnier in 1997 and for the centre for art and media technology (ZKM) in Karlsruhe. She then built up a continual presence as a club DJ from 2000 above all in her new home town of Hamburg. In particular her resident event &quot;Kill them all&quot; in the Hamburg Gum Club or her performances in Waagenbau (a nightclub in Hamburg) gained Xenia a reputation as one of the hottest DJ insider tips of the hanseatic city.','XENIA BELIAYEVA SIGNED TO RANDOM NOIZE MUSICK','\"I have always sung, and for about four years I have been building my vocals into my deejaying as a central element. Of course I see myself first and foremost as a DJ for electronic music, or Techno to be more precise, but I dont want to limit myself to this role.\"','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2010-02-23 00:00:00','2010-02-22 23:00:00','',0,'',33,'post','',0),
 (364,1,'2010-04-26 00:00:00','2010-04-25 23:00:00','','GOOD NEWS EYERYONE!!!','SHITKATAPULT was voted as BEST LABEL at this year\'s edition of QWARTZ AWARDS!!!\r\n\r\nwe would like to say THANK YOU  to everybody who voted for us and/or supported us in any way!!\r\n\r\nYOU ROCK AND TOGETHER WE ROLL!!\r\n\r\nand as a special thank you gesture we are offering a SPRING SALE!!\r\n\r\ncheck www.shopkatapult.com','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',37,'post','',0),
 (365,1,'2010-08-25 00:00:00','2010-08-24 23:00:00','','FREE TRACK by SCHIERES','Here\'s a brand new and unreleased track by Schieres feat. Miss Tigra, \"Level\", for free download. You\'ll get it by rightclick on the picture or headline. Have fun with this phantastic track. And don\'t forget to check out the video to \"Level\" on youtube.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',45,'post','',0),
