 (367,1,'2010-05-04 00:00:00','2010-05-03 23:00:00','','NEW ARTIST AND FREE DOWNLOAD','Welcome SID LE ROCK on Shitkatapult!!! He will release his new album \"Tout Va Bien\" in late June. Via clicking on the headline you get a free track STILL LIFE ready for download!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',38,'post','',0);
