 (368,1,'2010-05-05 00:00:00','2010-05-04 23:00:00','<p>We are totally happy that Sid Le Rock signed to Random Noize Musick recently. He will release a new album, too, on Shitkatapult in late June \'10, titled &quot;Tout Va Bien&quot;. </p><p>For all the friends/fans/folks who cannot wait so long, here\'s a new track off his upcoming album, <a href=\"information.php?info_id=15\">STILL LIFE</a> , ready for <a href=\"information.php?info_id=15\">free download</a> .</p><p>Here are some links to find out more:<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.sidlerock.com/cms/website.php?id=/de/news_detail_sub1.html\">www.sidlerock.com</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/rockno\">www.myspace.com/rockno</a> <br /></p>','SID LE ROCK SIGNED TO RANDOM NOIZE MUSICK','Random Noize Musick welcomes SID LE ROCK aka PAN/TONE on board.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2010-05-16 00:00:00','2010-05-15 23:00:00','',0,'',40,'post','',0),
 (369,1,'2010-06-04 00:00:00','2010-06-03 23:00:00','','SHITPARADE - July 3rd','THANK YOU ALL for coming to our Shitparade 2010!!!!! Hope, you all had a good time - definitely we had! And also a \"high five\" to Soul Center, Sid Le Rock, T.Raumschmiere, Fenin, Phon.o, Strobocop, Daniel Meteo, and Frank Bretschneider for joining, and Daniel and all at Club Maria for making this possible. See you next year!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2010-07-06 00:00:00','2010-07-05 23:00:00','',0,'',41,'post','',0),
 (370,1,'2010-07-16 00:00:00','2010-07-15 23:00:00','','SOUL CENTER EP OUT NOW','GE01 is the name of the new EP by Soul Center aka Thomas Brinkmann. In September, we will release his brandnew album \"General Eclectics\", but let\'s start with the 12 inches of GE01 which reverses the tracklisting and kicks off with Soul Center\'s sure-fire floor filler. Fun is a hot gun.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',43,'post','',0),
