 (372,1,'2010-07-02 00:00:00','2010-07-01 23:00:00','We are very proud that Thomas Brinkmann aka Soul Center signed to us. He just released his new EP on Shitkatapult, <a title=\"GE01\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shitkatapult.com/index.php?page=releaseinfo&amp;products_id=3884\">GE 01</a> , to feed the world with brand new and very hot tracks. He will also release the album GENERAL ECLECTICS on Shitkatapult, September the11th. And as far as I can tell you now: It\'s gonna be H O T ! ! ! <br />','SOUL CENTER SIGNED','SOUL CENTER aka THOMAS BRINKMANN is the new artist signed to Random Noize Musick.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',42,'post','',0),
 (373,1,'2010-09-14 00:00:00','2010-09-13 23:00:00','','OUT NOW - SOUL CENTER - NEW ALBUM','The new album GENERAL ECLECTICS by Thomas Brinkmann aka SOUL CENTER is out now on Shitkatapult. Additionally, there is also the second EP vinyl GE02 available now. Get all at your local record dealer or directly at shopkatapult.com.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',46,'post','',0),
 (374,1,'2010-10-27 00:00:00','2010-10-26 23:00:00','','OUT NOW - XENIA BELIAYEVA - DUMPFE TRAEUME','Xenia Beliayeva returns with her new Digital-only-EP \"Dumpfe Traeume\". The title track is also featured in the German vampire movie WIR SIND DIE NACHT, starting Oct 28th at a cinema near you. The EP also features an exclusive instrumental version of \"Know Me\" off her latest album \"Ever Since\". Check it out!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',47,'post','',0),
 (375,1,'2010-11-05 00:00:00','2010-11-04 23:00:00','','NEW FENIN ALBUM & EP OUT NOW!!!','Our favorite Dub-, Reggae-, House- Hero Lars Fenin returns with his third album MIXES & MAXIS on Shitkatapult. Besides, there is also his new EP NONE OF THEM with two brilliant remixes by Robag Wruhme available now. Go, check it out!!!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',48,'post','',0),
 (376,1,'2010-11-05 00:00:00','2010-11-04 23:00:00','<p>-Oval is the new artist signed to Random Noize Musick</p><p>-New Random Noize Musick ready for licensing:</p><p>a: FENIN - new album: Mixes &amp; Maxis</p><p>b: FENIN - new EP: None Of Them (Robag Wruhme Remixes)</p><p>c: XENIA BELIAYEVA - new EP: Dumpfe Tr&auml;ume</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>More news to come soon....</p><p>Yours, Random Noize Musick&nbsp;</p>','Newsflash in November','Here are some news for all you guys out there:','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',49,'post','',0),
 (377,1,'2010-11-17 00:00:00','2010-11-16 23:00:00','<p>Here are some press quotes:</p><p>&quot;A triumphant return for Oval, both musically and intellectually. This is meta music for the soul.&quot; - FACT Magazine<br /><br />&quot;Where there used to be glitches and electronic noise there are now guitars and drums. But that is the least important thing on &quot;O&quot;. What is truly relevant, his distinguished past aside, is that Oval has done it. Again. He has given birth to a record that could and should change the route of modern music.&quot; - Playgroundmag.net<br /><br />&quot;It\'s one mark of genius that the more you try to be different, the more you sound like yourself. It\'s wrong to overstate the continuities over the immediately obvious difference, but this music could only have been made by one man.&quot; - WIRE<br /><br />&quot;Incredibly, through a ten-year gap, complete shift in approach, software and even ideology, Popp has still managed to make what still sounds like an Oval album - possibly the best one of his career.&quot; - Exclaim.ca<br /><br />&quot;O is delicate and precise, supremely detailed and guided by beautiful, yearning melodies that evolve in slow motion (...)&nbsp; it\'s up there with 2010\'s best&quot;. - THE GUARDIAN<br /><br />&quot;The floating, lively and energetic music on these two formats simply cannot be passed over this year. Reinventing yourself can hardly be done any better.&quot; - De:Bug<br /><br />&quot;To call Oval an electronic music pioneer is like saying James Joyce &lsquo;kinda did things with novels.\'&quot; -The Stool Pigeon <br /><br />&quot;That Popp is able to work all these elements into anything remotely rhythmic is testament to his programming skills; that the end result is so endlessly listenable, is miraculous. &quot;New start&quot; or not, O is a work of vibrant and often brutal beauty that proves good things really do come to those who wait.&quot; - The Quietus<br /><br />&quot;Bela Bartok, John Cage, Brian Eno. And...Oval.&quot; - SPEX<br /><br />&nbsp;&quot;The new Oval sounds clean and quick, with each pluck, quiver, and beat standing out in stark relief... O is not a retro move, but the work of an artist dealing with the now.&quot; - Dusted<br /><br />&quot;A guitar dangling over his shoulder and equipped with a remarkably unconventional approach to harmony, Popp is doing things his own way, walking hand in hand with his laptop and finding the perfect medium between personal expression and computer-aided composition.&quot; - Tokafi.com <br /><br />&quot;Oval\'s double CD O is deliberately enigmatic yet immediately entertaining, nothing short of a small masterpiece.&quot; - YourFlesh Mag<br /><br />&quot;Listened to closely, each track reveals a precise and jewel-like structure, while in it totality, O refuses any intimation of form that might restrict the experience of listening to it. With its constant changes in tempo, O appears to stretch time elastically, becoming seemingly endless.&quot; - BBC Music Review<br /><br />&quot;It\'s lovely, it\'s pleasantly unsettling... It takes a very different route from his earlier work. If it ends up in a very similar place that just suggests his musical sensibilities have been asserting themselves all along.&quot; - Pitchfork<br /><br />&quot;Popp is smart enough to achieve the unheard, deft enough to have a signature sound without doing the same thing over and over again. Like Eno 20-plus years ago, his work is not only superlative, fascinating and totally listenable, it\'s a template for future research.&quot; - Mike McGonigal <br /><br />&nbsp;  <br /></p>','New album by OVAL','Oval, Random Noize Musick\'s latest artist, released his new album O in various formats on ThrillJockey: as 2-CD, double LP and Oh-EP; altogether 76 Tracks!!!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',50,'post','',0),
 (378,1,'2010-12-22 00:00:00','2010-12-21 23:00:00','','SHITKATAPULT GIFT !!!','Shitkatapult empfiehlt 3 - incl exclusive and unreleased tracks by T.RAUMSCHMIERE, TOM THIEL, FENIN, ISMAEL PINKLER free download until 31 dec 2010 - we wish you all happy holidays and hope to see you again in 2011 with new releases by SID LE ROCK, TOM THIEL, FRANK BRETSCHNEIDER, MARK BOOMBASTIK, WARREN SUICIDE and APPARAT to name just a few. thanks for your support!!! yours surely mad ants from berlin, SHITKATAPULT','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2010-12-22 00:00:00','2010-12-21 23:00:00','',0,'',51,'post','',0),
 (379,1,'2011-01-11 00:00:00','2011-01-10 23:00:00','','WELCOME 2011 !!!','Happy new year everyone! We start the year 2011 with this fine new ep \"Tout Va Plus\" by SID LE ROCK. This one bridges the gap between his last album TOUT VA BIEN and his upcoming brand new ep GENTLEMEN\'S INTERMISSION, due out in March. Check it out!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2011-01-11 00:00:00','2011-01-10 23:00:00','',0,'',52,'post','',0),
 (380,1,'2011-03-08 00:00:00','2011-03-07 23:00:00','','FRANK BRETSCHNEIDER - KOMET','Out now: The new album \"Komet\" by Frank Bretschneider. Seven tracks, which have been recorded and arranged live at the studio; seven tracks with an enormous depth and passion and love for detail on a straight beat, manifesting their own version of club music.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',53,'post','',0),
 (381,1,'2011-03-08 00:00:00','2011-03-07 23:00:00','','NEW ALBUM BY TOM THIEL','Tom Thiel\'s self titled debut album out now!!! Wide melody lines, soft, complex beats or direct, simple beats: the tracks speak a timeless language and thus represent the most modern side of electronic music. A musical director and his audio cinema, way beyond Hollywood or worse - New German Cinema.','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',54,'post','',0),
 (382,1,'2011-04-15 00:00:00','2011-04-14 23:00:00','','BRAND NEW - SID LE ROCK EP','Sid Le Rock (aka Pan/Tone) returns with his new EP Gentlemen\'s Intermission! Two brand new tracks and a fabolous remix of Made For You (originally from TOUT VA BIEN) by SOUL CENTER. Go check it out!!!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','2011-04-15 00:00:00','2011-04-14 23:00:00','',0,'',55,'post','',0),
 (383,1,'2011-05-31 00:00:00','2011-05-30 23:00:00','','NEW ALBUM OUT NOW: ADIOS BERLIN!','Mark Boombastik & Eduardo Delgado Lopez\'s first album on Shitkatapult out now: \"Adios Berlin\" is an album like a speech, between accapella and beatbox, punk and rough cut - techno and experiments for a special audience aka Special Musick For Special People!!!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',56,'post','',0),
 (384,1,'2011-05-31 00:00:00','2011-05-30 23:00:00','','T.RAUMSCHMIERE IS BACK!!!','His new EP titled THE RAVE IS ON is out now on Shitkatapult / Boxon Records. Three brand new rockers + a handful of remixes by Soul Center, Dilemn, Fukkk Offf and Pro7. Each music addict will be happy with this pack, as the first ones are especially for the dancefloor and the last on, \"Duster\" is a pretty experimental track. But check it out by yourself!','publish','open','open','','post_name','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'',57,'post','',0),
